nal/daily/article/20120829/18002608\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20120829%2F18002608&d=kjYWGV%2FOxf%2BJAuwkXUN1dCvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=5551e0b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20120829%2F18002608&h=24a56f2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20120829/18002608</a><br />\n<br />\n手術後腎消失 農婦尋腎3年無果<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2015/01/29/a1172952.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2015%2F01%2F29%2Fa1172952.html&d=kjYWGV%2FOxf%2BJAuwkXUN1dCvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=07782ec2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2015/01/29/a1172952.html</a><br />\n<br />\n包皮手術割一半醫生停下加價1萬5！ 病人負傷起來繳費<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/882584-中國-包皮手術割一半醫生停下加價1萬5！+病人負傷起來繳費\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F882584-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%8C%85%E7%9A%AE%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E5%89%B2%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%8A%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%81%9C%E4%B8%8B%E5%8A%A0%E5%83%B91%E8%90%AC5%EF%BC%81%2B%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E8%B2%A0%E5%82%B7%E8%B5%B7%E4%BE%86%E7%B9%B3%E8%B2%BB&d=kjYWGV%2FOxf%2BJAuwkXUN1dCvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=2f91438d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F882584-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%8C%85%E7%9A%AE%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E5%89%B2%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%8A%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%81%9C%E4%B8%8B%E5%8A%A0%E5%83%B91%E8%90%AC5%EF%BC%81%2B%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E8%B2%A0%E5%82%B7%E8%B5%B7%E4%BE%86%E7%B9%B3%E8%B2%BB&h=c41842b2\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/882584-中國-包皮手術割一半醫生停下加價1萬5！+病人負傷起來繳費</a><br />\n<br />\n重慶醫生手術途中突加碼 費用飆升13倍<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20151130/bkncn-20151130041046031-1130_05011_001.html